			<HEADING>Chapter 54: Community Right-To-Know Law Penalty Schedule</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-15822" name="T15C054"/>Chapter 54: Community Right-To-Know Law Penalty Schedule</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-114270" number="36216" version="1396">
								<HEADING>§ 54-01 General.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-15820" name="T15C054_54-01"/>§ 54-01 General.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114269" number="36217" version="2297">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>For the purposes of this chapter, the term Extremely Hazardous Substance (EHS) has the same meaning as provided by § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="24-702" destination-id="0-0-0-0">24-702</LINK>(h) of the Administrative Code. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114290" number="36218" version="2297">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Whenever a respondent is found in violation of any of the following provisions of the Administrative Code or the rules of the City of New York, any civil penalties recommended by a hearing officer, pursuant to 48 RCNY § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T48C006_6-17" destination-id="0-0-0-11561">6-17</LINK>(a) in accordance with Section <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="1813066185-672468487-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Charter.NFO" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="1049-a" destination-id="0-0-0-0">1049-a</LINK>(d)(1)(d) of the Charter and/or any civil penalties imposed for admissions of violations pursuant to 48 RCNY § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T48C006_6-09" destination-id="0-0-0-11539">6-09</LINK>(a) or late admissions pursuant to 48 RCNY § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T48C003_3-17" destination-id="0-0-0-11433">3-17</LINK> will be imposed pursuant to the penalty schedule set forth below. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114289" number="36219" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(c)<TAB tab-count="1"/>A second or subsequent offense is a violation by the same respondent of the same section within five years of the prior violation. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114288" number="36220" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(d)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Mitigating and Aggravating Factors: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114287" number="36221" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>All additions and subtractions are cumulative, except that factors J and K cannot be applied together, and factors A, B, and L may only be applied when at least one aggravating factor is also present (i.e., they cannot be used to reduce the penalty to less than the legal minimum). <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114286" number="36222" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Where the application of multiple aggravating factors would cause the legal maximum penalty to be exceeded, the legal maximum penalty (same as the default penalty) shall be imposed. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114285" number="36223" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>A.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Subtract $1,750 for compliance by first hearing date. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114284" number="36224" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>B.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Subtract $3,750 for compliance by first hearing date. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114283" number="36225" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>C.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Add $250 if there are any EHS stored at the facility. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114282" number="36226" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>D.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Add $1,750 if there are any EHS stored at the facility. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114281" number="36227" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>E.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Add $3,750 if there are any EHS stored at the facility. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114280" number="36228" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>F.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Add $100 for each unlabeled non-EHS hazardous substance more than one; add $2,000 for each unlabeled EHS. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114279" number="36229" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>G.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Add $1,000 if there are 25 or more hazardous substances stored at the facility; add $5,000 if there are more than 50 hazardous substances stored at the facility or if any EHS are stored at the facility. NOTE: This factor may only be applied until the legal maximum penalty has been reached. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114278" number="36230" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>H.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Add $5,000 for willful refusal to allow access to the facility, or physical interference with or obstruction of the inspection. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114277" number="36231" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>I.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Add $1,000 if there was an emergency response to the facility. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114276" number="36232" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>J.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Add $2,500 if there was a release of a hazardous substance at the facility. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114275" number="36233" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>K.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Add $4,500 if release of a hazardous substance at the facility resulted in injury to any person, or injury to plant or animal life, or damage to property or business. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114274" number="36234" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>L.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Subtract $250 where the existence of the violation was voluntarily disclosed to DEP by respondent. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114273" number="36235" version="1396">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>M.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Mitigate to zero where correction certified within 30 days of summons issuance. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114268" number="36236" version="1396">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 3/6/2019, eff. 4/5/2019) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
